msgid "Windows 10 on a Virtual Machine"
msgstr ""

#: ../fido2/windows/index.rst:227
msgid "Please keep in mind Nitrokey has internal timeout for accepting the FIDO reset operation of 10 seconds since powering up. If the Nitrokey will connect to a virtual machine later than that, it will return error and the operation will be aborted."
